songs.lyrics:
Forgive me for struggling (Repeated 3X)
It’s not…

Forgive me for struggling (Repeated 3X)
Forgive me…please

Forgive me for struggling (Repeated 3X)
It’s not…

Forgive me for struggling (Repeated 3X)
Forgive me…please

Forgive me for strugglin' (Repeated 3X)
It’s not…

He shoulda listened
Every brother, would you tap another brother and say
“I shoulda listened to her”
songs.title: Forgive Me
